languages.text: "Мы не незнакомцы друг другу, {name}. Мы — соратники, прошедшие многое. Ничто из свершенного не было забыто".
"We are no strangers to each other, {name}. We are fighting the same fight and have been through a great deal together. None of what we have achieved has been forgotten."

languages.text: “我们对彼此并不陌生，{name}。我们正在参加同一场战斗，也一起经历了很多事情。我们所成就的一切都没有被遗忘。”

languages.text: «No somos precisamente desconocidos, {name}. Luchamos la misma batalla y hemos pasado por mucho juntos. No olvido nada de lo que hemos atravesado».
languages.original_text: "We are no strangers to each other, {name}. We are fighting the same fight and have been through a great deal together. None of what we have achieved has been forgotten."

traits.speaker: PascalCompanion

languages.text: 「私たちはお互いに見知らぬ相手ではないのだ、{name}。私たちは同じ戦いをしているし、共に多くのことを経験してきた。私たちが成し遂げてきたことのどれも忘れてはいない」
languages.original_text: "We are no strangers to each other, {name}. We are fighting the same fight and have been through a great deal together. None of what we have achieved has been forgotten."

traits.speaker: PascalCompanion

languages.text: "Wir sind einander nicht fremd, {name}. Wir kämpfen denselben Kampf und haben viel gemeinsam durchgestanden. Nichts von dem, was wir erreicht haben, wurde vergessen."

languages.text: « Nous ne sommes pas des étrangers, {name}. Nous menons le même combat et avons connu bien des péripéties, vous et moi. Je n'ai rien oublié de nos exploits. »
